data.description: VA buyers have an AMAZING opportunity to assume an INCREDIBLY low rate of 2.375%!!! Don't miss the opportunity to own this exquisite brick duplex townhome in the sought-after Jefferson Manor neighborhood. Boasting a spacious lot with an extended driveway, this home offers the perfect blend of charm and modern updates. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the elegant hardwood floors that gracefully flow throughout the first two levels, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The main level is a true showstopper, featuring an updated kitchen with a delightful open layout. The kitchen is equipped with sleek shaker cabinets, quartz countertops, and modern appliances, making it a chef's dream and a perfect space for hosting friends and family. Moving to the upper level, you'll discover two well-appointed bedrooms, offering cozy retreats after a long day. A full bathroom on this level ensures convenience for all residents and guests. Additionally, the basement, with its convenient walk-up access, provides extra living space and includes another full bathroom, perfect for a variety of uses such as a home office, guest suite, or entertainment area. One of the standout features of this home is its lack of HOA fees, allowing you the freedom to make this property truly your own. Beyond the confines of this charming home, you'll find that it's ideally situated for easy commuting and access to all the amenities the area has to offer. The Huntington Metro Station, I-495, Rt 1, Rt 241, Old Town Alexandria, and downtown DC are all within easy reach, making this an excellent location for those who want to enjoy the best of the DMV area. This is an opportunity you won't want to miss. Schedule your visit today to experience this remarkable Jefferson Manor townhome for yourself, and imagine the possibilities it holds for your future.
